overview: “COMEDY CENTRAL’s Last Laugh ’05” takes an irreverent look back at some of the most controversial and outrageous events of this year from the infamous Tom Cruise couch dance to the Terri Schiavo saga, bird flu to Courtney Love’s melt-down, “Last Laugh ’05” unleashes its fury on our most laughable newsmakers and news fakers.
tagline: ONE MIND-BLOWING YEAR CRAMMED INTO ONE NIGHT OF COMEDY AND MUSIC
title: Last Laugh '05
